Ускорение

In [318]:
def add_speed_up_column(df):
    df = df.astype({'time': float})
    df_1 = df[df.treads.isin([1])]
    speed_up = []
    for i in df[df.treads.isin([1])].dim:
        speed_up.append(np.array(np.array(df_1[df_1.dim.isin([i])].time)/df[df.dim.isin([i])].time))
    speed_up_new = []
    for i in range(len(speed_up)):
        for j in range(len(speed_up[i])):
            speed_up_new.append(speed_up[i][j])

    df["speed_up"] = speed_up_new
    return df
In [319]:
df_row_float = add_speed_up_column(df_row_float)
df_col_float = add_speed_up_column(df_col_float)
df_block_float = add_speed_up_column(df_block_float)
